Note on bundled assets:

The Semitic Stretch fonts under web/public/fonts/SemiticStretch*.ttf are
derivatives of upstream faces and retain their upstream licenses (SIL Open
Font License 1.1 or GNU GPL v2.0). See the per-font LICENSE sidecars in the
companion repository:

  https://github.com/andyagtech/semitic-stretch-fonts

Non-derivative bundled fonts (Noto*, Free*, EastSyriacNohadra, etc.) retain
their upstream OFL / GPL / public-domain licenses. See each font vendor's
site for the authoritative license text.

Third-party lexical data ingested from Kaikki.org, Wiktionary, and other
sources retains its upstream license (typically CC-BY-SA 4.0).
